{"tid":1150010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10蠱惑中學生截圖扮畀錢 被拆穿後賠$23,000","createTime":"2019-05-11T13:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:27:15.000Z","uid":78046,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f251502dfcf021b79c2a71fe9df3929158828f32","tid":1150010,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"在內地，幾乎人人都會手機電子錢包支付，用手機掃描二維碼後，向店家展示支付成功的頁面，以證明自己已經付錢。廣西省南寧市有10名高中生，利用微信支付成功的截圖欺騙餐廳老闆吃霸王餐，劣行還持續了1年。<br />\n事發在當地一間中學附近的餐廳，店主馬先生於4月10日及11日中午和下午，發現微信支付有異常，一名17歲的男生小強（化名），向他展示微信支付成功的頁面後，馬先生卻發現他收不到款項，於是追問小強，小強才拿出手機支付款項。小強承認，自去年6月開始，他就多次利用一張之前微信支付成功的截圖到馬先生的店用餐，此外，他還有9名同學多次用同樣手法到店內吃霸王餐。<br />\n馬先生隨後再檢查CCTV，發現小強是熟客，他在40多天內在店內消費60多次，按每次消費約20元人民幣（下同，約23港元）左右，理應已經支付上千元（約1,150港元），不過，小強的支付紀錄只有9次，共179元（約206港元）。涉事的10名學生承認多次吃霸王餐，經過調解，10名學生每人要向馬先生賠償2,000元（約2,300港元）。<br />\n馬先生說，有時他不在店內，收錢的店員收不到收款成功的語音提醒，有時因為店面繁忙，也沒核實顧客有沒有支付。<br />\n有網民看見學生的劣行，斥責「人家小本生意，這10名學生讀這麼多年的書，學到了甚麼？！貪小便宜？還好被店主抓到後承認了，好好吸取教訓，轉邪歸正吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2019/05/10/3826933/20190511_chi_26_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2019%2F05%2F10%2F3826933%2F20190511_chi_26_w.mp4&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=290941dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2019/05/10/3826933/20190511_chi_26_w.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"2c4f044bf11fbb2373bbb2613676ea19bf7a03a1","tid":1150010,"uid":67325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:03:54.000Z","msg":"只有騙子係真嘅國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e973e95279f5ef8cf08385bdb83349dc42f2dd3","tid":1150010,"uid":232594,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"又作大數呃人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ce8ccdf2158e5a46582f63fab7e16f82813426","tid":1150010,"uid":78046,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e973e95279f5ef8cf08385bdb83349dc42f2dd3","tid":1150010,"uid":232594,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"又作大數呃人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"邊有  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f6712c31130bd4027467db802a5b2975c985a2","tid":1150010,"uid":3598,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e973e95279f5ef8cf08385bdb83349dc42f2dd3","tid":1150010,"uid":232594,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"又作大數呃人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:06:55.000Z","msg":"10名學生每人要向馬先生賠償2,000元（約2,300港元）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10x2300=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3604211e6b37ba103d43513e0f08888a1c473d35","tid":1150010,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"樓豬on99"},{"pid":"0500c093e51cf5010f2eb7dbe9e8ea0908119c5f","tid":1150010,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"qr俾錢同八達通比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0832e3b0206a3941f9e56b55a4fdb2bea902e865","tid":1150010,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"馮本事食返嚟點解要還.jpeg"}]}